<section class="cta-final" id="contacto">
  <span class="blob b1" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  <span class="blob b2" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  <span class="blob b3" aria-hidden="true"></span>

  <div class="container">
    <h2>No esperes a que todo se derrumbe</h2>
    <p>¿List@ para dar el primer paso? Solo es una conversación. Sin compromiso, sin tener que tenerlo todo claro.</p>
    <a class="btn" href="https://calendly.com/adrianapsicologia/15-20min" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      Reservar primera sesión →
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.cta-final {
  position: relative;
  background: var(--color-moss);
  color: var(--color-text-inverse);
  padding: var(--space-16) 0;
  text-align: center;
  overflow: hidden;
}

/* ── Blobs decorativos ── */
.blob {
  position: absolute;
  pointer-events: none;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,.6);
  border-radius: 50%;
}
.b1 { width: 240px; height: 240px; left: -80px;  top: -100px;          opacity: .18; }
.b2 { width: 160px; height: 160px; right: 6%;    top: 30%;             opacity: .12; }
.b3 { width: 300px; height: 300px; right: -120px; bottom: -160px;       opacity: .14; }

.container {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 var(--gutter);
}

h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: var(--fs-h2);
  font-weight: var(--fw-semi);
  line-height: var(--lh-heading);
  letter-spacing: var(--ls-tight);
  margin: 0 0 var(--space-4);
  color: #fff;
}

p {
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: var(--fs-body-lg);
  line-height: var(--lh-body);
  margin: 0 auto var(--space-8);
  max-width: 54ch;
  opacity: 0.92;
  color: #fff;
}

.btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  height: 52px;
  padding: 0 var(--space-8);
  background: var(--color-bg-base);
  color: var(--color-text-primary);
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: var(--fs-body-sm);
  font-weight: var(--fw-semi);
  border-radius: var(--radius-full);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background var(--transition-fast), transform var(--transition-fast);
}
.btn:hover {
  background: var(--color-bg-soft);
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}

@media (min-width: 880px) {
  .cta-final {
    padding: var(--space-20) 0;
  }
  h2 { font-size: var(--fs-h1); }
}
</style>
